The paper deals with face alignment, which is a common problem in computer vision and falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel approach using an ensemble of models, which involves machine learning techniques and falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its approach on a large number of face images, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
